    <h1>TeamGym</h1>
    <p>TRICKS is one of the strongest teams in the nation representing TeamGym. Gymnasts compete in a group in two events; Floor ex and Jump. The Jump routine consists of tumbling, vault and mini tramp.</p>
		<p>TeamGym is an exciting genre of gymnastics!  These teams have competed in New York, Texas, So Cal, Las Vegas and have even participated in World Gymnastrada in Spain.</p>
		<p>Most meets are local.  We travel to one away meet plus Nationals for qualifying teams.</p>
		<p>All levels of athletes can participate. The season starts in July and ends in June. Try outs are the end of June.</p>
  </div>
